  DO NOT EDIT THIS FILE
  ============================================================================
  This file is a COLD-START FALLBACK ONLY. Edits made here are IGNORED at
  runtime as soon as HemoScope can reach the cloud config repo.

  Edit the live version in:
      https://github.com/LiteBC/Hemoscope-config

  Commit and push there. The bench picks up the change at the next launch
  (look for [ConfigSync] lines in HemoScope.log).

  This bundled copy exists only so the app can still boot when:
    - it is a fresh install with no local cache yet, AND
    - the cloud repo is unreachable (offline / GitHub down).
  ============================================================================
-->
